column2: SELECT TOP # w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3 FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecPhotoAll WHERE SpecPhotoAll.nChild = #) AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecObjAll WHERE SpecObjAll.z > # AND SpecObjAll.z < #) AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE (s.class = # or s.class = #)
